<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3814426>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Iberian Pungentus species. – A-C. Pungentus clavatus Ahmad & Jairajpuri, 1979. – D-H. Pungentus engadinensis (Altherr, 1950). – I-K. Pungentus marietani Altherr, 1950. – L-N. Pungentus silvestris Coomans & Geraert, 1962. – A, D, I, L. ♀, anterior region in lateral median view. B, E, J, M. ♀, genital system. C, G, K, N. ♀, posterior body region. F. ♂, posterior body region. H. ♀, caudal region." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3814426/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

